## Introduction
This open-source library is a political news crawler for 34 Taiwanese mainstream media.
The crawlered media is listed below.

Media Type|Meida Name (CN)|Media Name (EN)|ID|Abbreviation
:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:
